column1: # Required | A unique ID for the item. Use the SKU if you can. Enter each ID only once or the item won't upload. For dynamic ads; this ID must exactly match the content ID for the same item in your Facebook pixel. Character limit: 100.
column2: # Required | A specific; relevant title for the item. Include keywords such as brand; attributes or condition. Character limit: 150.
column3: # Required | A short; relevant description of the item. Include specific or unique product features such as material or colour. Use plain text and don't enter text in all capital letters. Character limit: 5;000.
column4: # Required | The current availability of the item in your shop. | Supported values: in stock; available for order; preorder; out of stock; discontinued
column5: # Required | The condition of the item. | Supported values: new; refurbished; used
column6: # Required | The cost and currency of the item. The price is a number followed by the 3-digit currency code (ISO 4217 standards). Use a full stop (".") as the decimal point.
column7: # Required | The URL of the specific product page where people can buy the item. If you don't have a URL; provide a fallback; such as a link to your Facebook business Page.
column8: # Required | The URL for the main image of your item. Use a square (1:1) format image with a resolution of 1024 x 1024 pixels or higher.
column9: # Required | The brand name; unique manufacturer part number (MPN) or Global Trade Item Number (GTIN) of the item. You only need to enter one of these; not all of them. For GTIN; enter the item's UPC; EAN; JAN or ISBN. Character limit: 100.
